---
const trackingFeatures = [
  'How many active subscriptions you have',
  'Monthly cost at a glance',
  'Annual cost (often the real wake-up call)',
  'Potential savings if you cancel unused services',
]
---

<section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-slate-50">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="font-display text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 text-center">
        Find the leaks.
      </h2>

      <div class="mt-10 max-w-2xl mx-auto space-y-6 text-lg text-slate-600">
        <p class="text-center">
          The average American spends over <span class="font-semibold text-slate-900">$200/month on subscriptions</span> â€” and most don't realize it.
        </p>
        <p class="text-center">
          Storehouse automatically detects your recurring charges and shows you:
        </p>
      </div>

      <ul class="mt-8 max-w-lg mx-auto space-y-4">
        {trackingFeatures.map((feature) => (
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3 p-4 bg-white rounded-xl border border-slate-200">
            <svg
              class="h-6 w-6 text-storehouse-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5"
              fill="none"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              stroke-width="2"
              stroke="currentColor"
            >
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
            </svg>
            <span class="text-slate-700">{feature}</span>
          </li>
        ))}
      </ul>

      <p class="mt-10 text-xl text-center text-slate-900 font-medium">
        Small leaks sink big ships. We help you spot them.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
